        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Fading from view, you unsettle your target with disturbing noises, whether sounds of a creature echoing in a cave or baleful whispers in their ear.</p><p><strong>Once Per Turn</strong>\u00a0- 1 Creature (120 ft)</p><p>You can use this feature when you use a spell to turn &amp;reference[invisible], &amp;reference[blinded]{blind} a creature, or otherwise prevent your target from seeing you.</p><p>Dealing damage with this feature does not end the <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.vWQiuirTFxetH3lm]{Invisibility}</em> spell.</p><p><strong>Wisdom Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d8 psychic]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul>",
